    "body": "Geth usually waits a bit for the consensus client to attach and start sending some exchanges. If it does not, it will complain. Let it run for a while and see if the complaints remain. According to the spec the consensus client should ping us every minute at max for a ttd config exchange. We first wait 30 secs, then 5 minutes after for this exchange and keep warning until we see it,",
